ves that small farmers in Africa are the key to achieving sustainable development, for which a bottom-up approach is crucial. She is currently works with DIBcoop, an International Business development as Director Rwanda Office and she has previous worked with SHER-Rwanda, MDF among other where she gained experience in natural resource management, environmental protection, working with farmers and in construction. She contributes to the DIBcoop team in Rwanda by supporting community engagement processes, developing and implementing integrated water catchment plans, and assisting with M&amp;E reporting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"shadow\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"50px\",\"right\":\"2.5em\",\"bottom\":\"70px\",\"left\":\"2.5em\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#f3faf8\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"10px\",\"right\":\"10px\",\"bottom\":\"10px\",\"left\":\"10px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"50{3338937df10194424d40636f8c2716dc2160f64fc18487a5744941c2d65e9ddb}\",\"width\":\"2px\"}},\"borderColor\":\"cyan-bluish-gray\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":78,\"width\":\"118px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure><img style=\"width: 118px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://ciac.rw/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IMG-1232_JPG.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"0px\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"20px\",\"right\":\"20px\",\"bottom\":\"20px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"white\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":4,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"letterSpacing\":\"1px\"}},\"fontSize\":\"regular\"} -->\n<h4 style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Nduwayezu Leon</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"10px\"}}},\"textColor\":\"primary\"} -->\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px;\"><strong><em>BoD member, founder and Disciplinary Committee President</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:details --><details>\n<summary><strong>E-mail:</strong><br /><a href=\"mailto:nduluwa@yahoo.fr\">nduluwa@yahoo.fr</a><br /><strong>Mobile/WhatsApp:</strong><br /> (250)788300629<br /><strong>Languages: </strong><br />English, French, Kinyarwanda</summary>\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details><!-- /wp:details -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"shadow\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Leon Nduwayezu is an ambitious innovator who aims to resolve Rwanda’s agricultural packaging problems. Currently, many small holder farmers in Rwanda struggle to deliver safely and securely their fresh produce across the country. With a background in strategic planning and marketing, Leon Nduwayezu has decided to end the packaging problem in Rwandan agro-industry sector by starting AgroPlast Ltd, a company that has been manufacturing net bags since 2015. These bags are used to transport and export mainly potatoes, but also fruits and vegetables are targeted.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n<!-- /wp:columns --><!-- wp:separator --><hr /><!-- /wp:separator --><!-- wp:columns -->\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"shadow\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"50px\",\"right\":\"2.5em\",\"bottom\":\"70px\",\"left\":\"2.5em\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#f3faf8\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"10px\",\"right\":\"10px\",\"bottom\":\"10px\",\"left\":\"10px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"50{3338937df10194424d40636f8c2716dc2160f64fc18487a5744941c2d65e9ddb}\",\"width\":\"2px\"}},\"borderColor\":\"cyan-bluish-gray\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":80,\"width\":\"104px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure><img style=\"width: 104px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://ciac.rw/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/cia.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"0px\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"20px\",\"right\":\"20px\",\"bottom\":\"20px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"white\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":4,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"letterSpacing\":\"1px\"}},\"fontSize\":\"regular\"} -->\n<h4 style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong>NTIGURA Jean Ferdinand</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"10px\"}}},\"textColor\":\"primary\"} -->\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px;\"><strong><em>BoD member, founder and Disciplinary Committee Vice President</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:details {\"align\":\"wide\"} --><details>\n<summary><strong>Email:</strong><br />jntigura@gmail.com<br /><strong>Mobile/WhatsApp:</strong><br />+250 783 797 205 (Rw)<strong><br />Skype Name:</strong><br />Ntigura Jean Ferdinand<br /><strong>Languages: </strong><br />English, French, Kinyarwanda</summary>\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details><!-- /wp:details -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"shadow\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ferdinand holds Bachelor degree in Quantity Surveying and has over 10 years’ experience in construction industry. Registered, Member of Rwanda Institute of Quantity Surveyor (RIQS), Private and Personnel engaged in business activities. He worked with various construction companies, consultants and developers in Rwanda. He also worked as Civil Servant and holds Local Community responsibilities. Her gained experience and skills help in natural resource management, environmental protection, working with community and construction as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"shadow\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"50px\",\"right\":\"2.5em\",\"bottom\":\"70px\",\"left\":\"2.5em\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#f3faf8\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"10px\",\"right\":\"10px\",\"bottom\":\"10px\",\"left\":\"10px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"50{3338937df10194424d40636f8c2716dc2160f64fc18487a5744941c2d65e9ddb}\",\"width\":\"2px\"}},\"borderColor\":\"cyan-bluish-gray\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"\"}} -->\n \n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"0px\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"20px\",\"right\":\"20px\",\"bottom\":\"20px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"white\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"10px\"}}},\"textColor\":\"primary\"} -->\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px;\"> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:details --><details>\n<summary></summary>\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details><!-- /wp:details -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column -->\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"shadow\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:group -->","Our Team","","inherit","closed","closed","","72-revision-v1","","","2025-10-09 08:16:49","2025-10-09 08:16:49","","72","https://ciac.rw/?p=138","0","revision","","0");
INSERT INTO `oJegmj1Sz_posts` VALUES("139","1","2025-10-09 08:18:52","2025-10-09 08:18:52","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a><strong>Organisational background and capacity</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CIAC has been established in January 2022 with the overall goal of contributing to the promotion of Rwandan communities by improving livelihood through efficient use of natural resources and promoting environmentally friendly agriculture for sustainable development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CIAC is a non-profit making non-governmental organization based in Kigali city and it is operating in Rwanda CIAC is serving small farmers, especially women and youth cooperatives.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CIAC’s intervention domains</strong>:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Environment management.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Climate change adaptation and mitigation .</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Conflict management</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Economic development.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Good governance</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Organizational structure:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The management structure of CIAC is composed of the General Assembly, the Board of Directors, and the Coordination Unit which designs and coordinates all project activities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CIAC has a management committee that follows regularly the use of funds as they are acquired from various donors for the implementation of different projects, CIAC manages those funds according to their source and the norms of the donor. The internal financial and technical reports are produced monthly, quarterly, and annually. The external audit is made annually and other reports are made when needed or according to the convention with the donors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All reports are made at the level of coordination and approved by the Representative of CIAC. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Previous   and current activities of CIAC include:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Conflict reduction among the farmer family in the Mugina sector</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Provision of improved cooking stoves to small farmers in Kayonza District with AGROPLAST Lts</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tree planting in Rukeri landscape.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->","CIAC Background","","inherit","closed","closed","","50-autosave-v1","","","2025-10-09 08:18:52","2025-10-09 08:18:52","","50","https://ciac.rw/?p=139","0","revision","","0");
INSERT INTO `oJegmj1Sz_posts` VALUES("144","1","2025-10-22 07:25:33","2025-10-22 07:25:33","<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"https://ciac.rw/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/53299587626_c3909a21ca_k.jpg\",\"id\":9,\"dimRatio\":0,\"isDark\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-light\"><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-9\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ciac.rw/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/53299587626_c3909a21ca_k.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"/><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"60px\",\"right\":\"20px\",\"bottom\":\"60px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"padding-top:60px;padding-right:20px;padding-bottom:60px;padding-left:20px\"><!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"var:preset|color|primary\"}}},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"0px\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"20px\",\"right\":\"20px\",\"bottom\":\"40px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"12px\"},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#061733\"}},\"textColor\":\"primary\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-primary-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color\" style=\"border-radius:12px;background-color:#061733;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding-top:20px;padding-right:20px;padding-bottom:40px;padding-left:20px\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":null} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"fontSize\":\"regular\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-regular-font-size\">Contact CIAC Rwanda</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-